    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the tea sounds nice but i'm still feeling really heavy in my chest and it's making me feel a bit sick to my stomach. i dont want to go to the doctor if i don't have to, it's such a hassle. do you think it's safe if i just take a double dose of the propranolol to make sure the anxiety actually goes away? i just want to feel normal again.",
